Class TMDbUtility.PROVIDERS

java.lang.Object
fi.tuni.swdesign.movienightplanner.utilities.TMDbUtility.PROVIDERS
Enclosing class:
TMDbUtility
private final class TMDbUtility.PROVIDERS extends Object
Represents a collection of provider IDs for streaming services supported by the application. Each constant field represents a unique provider identifier.
